String.tooltip: The target suffers continuous electric shocks upon a successful hit.

String.name: Electric Shock
String.tooltip: Targets hit with Electric Shock suffer disjointed movements on an ongoing basis, and some skills are restricted.

String.name: Toxa Poisoning
String.tooltip: You are poisoned at regular intervals after a Toxa Monolith is summoned.$BR- Toxa Poisoning increases the damage you take by 7.5% and can be stacked up to 8 times.$BR- The affliction is lifted upon death. You can't be poisoned at the base.

String.name: Curse of Oppression
String.tooltip: You don't have permission to challenge this dungeon. Physical/Magic Amplification and Resistance are dramatically reduced. Can be removed by increasing item level.
